<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/52049120-the-scourge-of-war"><img alt="The Scourge of War: The Life of William Tecumseh Sherman" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1569581480l/52049120._SX98_SY160_.jpg" />
